hadiths[44]{hadithnumber,text}:
2738,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kisi musalman ke liye jinke paas wasiiyat ke qaabil koi bhi maal ho durust nahi ke 2 raat bhi wasiiyat ko likh kar apne paas mehfooz rakhey baghair guzaarey.'' Imam Malik ke sath is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Muhammad-bin-Muslim ne Amr-bin-Dinar se ki hai, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki hai."
2739,"aur unse Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke nisbatii bhai Amr-bin-Haris (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo Juweriya binte- Haris (Raziallahu anhu)) Ummul-Momenin (ke bhai hain, bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni wafat ke baad siwaey apne safaid khachchar , apne hathiyar aur apni zameen ke jisey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) waqf kar gaey they na koi dirham chhoda tha na Dinar na ghulam na baandi aur na koi cheez ."
2740,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi wasiiyat ki thi? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi. is par maine puchha ke phir wasiiyat kis tarah logon par farz huii? ya ( rawi ne is tarah bayan kya (ke logon ko wasiiyat ka hukm kyon kar diya gayaa? unhon-ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko kitabullah par amal karne ki wasiiyat ki thi.
2741,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan kuchh logon ne zikr kya ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke) wasii they, to aap ne kaha ke Kab unhein wasii banaya. main to aap ke wisaal ke waqt sar Mubarak apne seeney par ya unhon-ne (bajaaey seeney ke) kaha ke apne god mein rakhey huey thi phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (pani ka ( tasht mangwaya tha ke itney main ( sar Mubarak ( meri god mein jhuk gaya aur main samajh na saki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho chuki hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko wasii Kab banaya."
2742,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (hijjatul-wadaa mein) meri iyaadat ko tashrif laaey, mein us waqt Makka mein tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us sar-zameen par maut ko pasand nahi farmatey they jahan se koi hijrat kar chuka ho. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allaah-ibn-Ifraa (Sa'd bin Khaula (Raziallahu anhu)) par raham farmaaey.'' mein arz kya ya Rasulullah ! main apne sarey maal w daulat ki wasiiyat kar dun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' nahi '' maine puchha phir aadhey ki kar dun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par bhi yahi farmaya '' nahi '' maine puchha phir tehai ki kar dun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tehai ki kar saktey ho aur ye bhi bahut hai, agar tum apne waarison ko apne peechhey maaldaar chhodo to ye us se behtar hai ke unhein mohtaaj chhodo ke logon ke samney hath phailaatey phirein, ismein koi shuba nahi ke jab tum apni koi cheez ( Allah ke liye kharch karogey ( to wo khairat hai, yahan tak ke wo luqma bhi jo tum apni biwi ke munh mein daalogey (wo bhi khairat hai) aur) abhi wasiiyat karne ki koi zarurat bhi nahi ( mumkin hai ke Allah Taala tumhen shifa de aur uske baad tum se bahut se logon ko fayda ho aur doosrey bahut se log (Islam ke mukhaalif) nuqsan uthaaein. us waqt Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ki sirf aik beti thi."
2743,kash! log (wasiiyat ko) chothai tak kam kar detey to behtar hota kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ''tum tehai (ki wasiiyat kar saktey ho) aur tehai bhi bahut hai.'' ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke) ''ye bahut zyada raqam hai.''
2744,main Makka mein bimar padaa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif laey. maine arz kya ya Rasulullah ! mere liye dua kijiye ke Allah mujhey ultey paon wapas na kar de (yani Makka mein meri maut na ho (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mumkin hai ke Allah Taala tumhen sihat de aur tum se bahut se log nafa uthaaein. maine arz kya mera irada wasiiyat karne ka hai. aik ladki ke siwa aur mere koi ( aulad ( nahi. maine puchha kya aadhey maal ki wasiiyat kar dun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aadha to bahut hai. phir maine puchha to tehai ki kar dun? farmaya ke tehai ki kar saktey ho agarche ye bhi bahut hai ya (ye farmaya ke) badi ( raqam ( hai. chunanche log bhi tehai ki wasiiyat karne lagey aur ye unke liye jaaiz ho gaee.
2745,"Utba-bin- abii-waqaas ne martey waqt apne bhai Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ko wasiiyat ki thi ke Zam-aa ki baandi ka ladka mera hai, isliye tum usey ley lena chunanche fateh Makka ke mauqe par Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey ley liya aur kaha ke mere bhai ka ladka hai. unhon-ne us barey mein mujhey uski wasiiyat ki thi. phir abd-bin-Zam'a (Raziallahu anhu) uthey aur kehney lagey ke ye to mera bhai hai mere bap ki londi ne usko janaa hai aur mere bap ke bistar par paida hua hai. phir ye donon Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! ye mere bhai ka ladka hai, mujhey us ne wasiiyat ki thi. lekin abd-bin-Zam'a (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke ye mera bhai aur mere walid ki baandi ka ladka hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne faisla ye farmaya ke ladka tumhara hi hai abd-bin-Zam'a ! bachcha faraash ke tehet hota hai aur zaanii ke hissey mein patthar hain lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Sauda-binte-Zama (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke us ladkey se parda kar kyonke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Utba ki mushabihat (similarity) us ladkey mein saaf paai thi. chunanche iske baad us ladkey ne Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ko kabhi na dekha yahan tak ke aap Allah Taala se ja miliin."
2746,aik Yahudi ne aik ( Ansari ( ladki ka sar 2 pattharon ke darmyan mein rakh kar kuchal diya tha. ladki se puchha gaya ke tumhara sar is tarah kis ne kya hai? kya falan shakhs ne kya? falan ne kya? aakhir Yahudi ka bhi naam liya gaya (jisne uska sar kuchal diya tha) to ladki ne sar ke ishaarey se haan mein jawab diya. phir wo Yahudi bulaya gaya aur aakhir usne bhi iqrar kar liya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se iska bhi patthar se sar kuchal diya gaya.
2747,"shuru Islam mein (meeraas ka ( maal aulad ko milta tha aur waalidain ke liye wasiiyat zaroori thi, lekin Allah Taala ne jis tarah chaha us hukm ko mansukh kar diya phir ladkey ka hissa 2 ladkiyon ke barabar qarar diya aur waalidain mein se har aik ka chhataa hissey aur biwi ka (aulaad ki maujoodgii mein) aathwaan hissey aur (aulaad ke na honey ki sura mein) chotha hissey qarar diya. isi tarah shauhar ka (aulaad na honey ki sura mein) aadha (aulaad honey ki sura mein) chothai hissey qarar diya."
2748,"aik sahabi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ya Rasulullah ! kon sa sadqa afzal hai? farmaya ye ke sadqe tandurustii ki haalat mein karke (tujh ko us maal ko baqi rakhney ki) khahish bhi ho jis se kuchh sarmaaya jama ho janey ki tumhen ummeed ho aur (usey kharch karne ki sura mein) mohtaajii ka dar ho aur is mein taakheer na karke jab Rooh halaq tak pahunch jaey to kehney baith jaey ke itna maal falan ke liye, fulaaney ko itna denaa, ab to fulaaney ka ho hi gaya (to to duniya se chalaa)."
2749,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''munaafiq ki teen nishaniyan hain jab baat kahey to jhoot kahey aur jab uske paas amanat rakhein to khayanat karey aur jab wada karey to khilaf kare.''
2750,"Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu)) mashhoor sahabi ( ne bayan kya maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maanga aap ne mujh ko diya, phir maanga phir aap ne diya, phir farmaney lagey hakeem ye duniya ka rupya-paisaa dekhney mein khushnumaa aur mazey mein meetha hai lekin jo koi usko sair chashmii se ley usko barkat hoti hai aur jo koi jaan lada kar hirs ke sath usko ley usko barkat na hogi. uski misal aisi hai jo kamaataa hai lekin sair nahi hota uper wala (dene wala) hath nichey waley (leney waale) hath se behtar hai. hakeem ne arz kya ya Rasulullah! qism uski jisne aapko sachcha paighambar karke bheja hai main to aaj se aap ke baad kisi se koi cheez kabhi nahi loonga marney tak phir ( hakeem ka ye haal raha (ke Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) unka saalaana wazeefa dene ke liye unko bulaatey, wo usko leney se inkar kartey. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi apni khilafat mein unko bulaya unka wazeefa dene ke liye lekin unhon-ne inkar kya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) kehney lagey musalmaanon ! tum gawah rehna hakeem ko uska haq jo ghaneemat ke maal mein Allah ne rakha hai deta hun wo nahi letaa. gharaz hakeem ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad phir kisi shakhs se koi cheez qabool nahi ki (apnaa wazeefa bhi baitul-maal mein na liyaa) yahan tak ke unki wafat ho gaee. Allah un par raham kare."
2751,"maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they tum mein se har koi nigahbaan hai aur apni raiyat ke barey mein puchha jaeyga Hakim bhi nigahbaan hai apni raiyat ke barey mein puchha jaeyga aur mard apne ghar walon ka nigahbaan hai aur apni raiyat ke barey mein puchha jaeyga aur aurat apne khawind ke ghar ki nigahbaan hai apni raiyat ke barey mein poochhi jaeygi aur ghulam apne sahib ke maal ka nigahbaan hai aur apni raiyat ke barey mein puchha jaeyga ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main samajhta hun Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye bhi farmaya ke mard apne bap ke maal ka nigahbaan hai aur apni raiyat ke barey mein puchha jaeyga"
2752,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Talha se farmaya (jab unhon-ne apna beerhaa ka baagh Allah ki raah mein dena chaha ( mein munasib samajhta hun to ye baagh apne azeezon ko de-dey. abu-Talha ne kaha bahut khub aisa hi karunga. phir abu-Talha ne wo baagh apne azeezon aur chacha ke beton mein taqseem kar diya aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha jab ( sura shau'raa ki) ye aayat utri ( وأنذر عشيرتك الأقربين‏ ( ""aur apne qareeb ke rishtedaron ko) Allah ke azab se) daraa"" to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Quraish ke khandanon bani fahar, bani Adi ko pukarney lagey ( unko daraayaa (aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha jab ye aayat utri ( وأنذر عشيرتك الأقربين‏ (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aey Quraish ke logo ! ( Allah se daro ( ."
2753,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha jab ( sura Shau'raa ki) ye aayat Allah Taala ne utari ( وأنذر عشيرتك الأقربين‏ (aur apne nazdeek rishtedaron ko Allah ke azab se dara to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Quraish ke logo! ya aisa hi koi aur kalima tum log apni apni jaanon ko (nek aamaal ke badal) mol ley lo (bachaa lo) mein Allah ke samney tumharey kuchh kaam nahi aaoonga (yani uski marzii ke khilaf main kuchh nahi kar sakoonga) abd munaaf ke beto! main Allah ke samney tumharey kuchh kaam nahi aaoonga. Abbas abdul-Muttalib ke betey! main Allah ke samney tumharey kuchh kaam nahi aaoonga. Safiya meri phoophii ! Allah ke samney tumharey kuchh kaam nahi aaoonga. Faatima! beti to chahey mera maal maang ley lekin Allah ke samney terey kuchh kaam nahi aaoonga. abul-Yamaan ke sath hadis ko asbagh ne bhi Abdullaah-bin-Wahab se, unhon-ne Yunus se, unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat kya."
2754,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha ke aik shakhs qurbani ka oont haankey liye ja raha hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya ke is par Sawar ho jaa. us sahib ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! ye qurbani ka oont hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teesri ya chothi baar farmaya afsos ! sawar bhi ho ja ya aap ne ( ويلك ( ki bajaey ( ويحك ( farmaya jiske mana bhi wahi hain.
2755,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha ke aik sahib qurbani ka oont haankey liye ja rahe hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is par Sawar ho ja lekin unhon-ne ma'zirat ki ke ya Rasulullah! ye to qurbani ka hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ke sawar bhi ho jaa. afsos! ye kalima Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teesri ya chothi martaba farmaya tha.
2756,Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ki maan Umra-binte-Mas'ood ka intiqal hua to wo unki khidmat mein maujood nahi they. unhon-ne aa kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ya Rasulullah! meri walida ka jab intiqal hua to main unki khidmat mein hazir nahi tha. kya agar main koi cheez sadqa karun to us se unhein fayda pahunch sakta hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab diya : haan. to unhon-ne kaha ke main aapko gawah banata hun ke mera mikhraaf naam ke baagh unki taraf se sadqa hai.
2757,"maine Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo bayan kartey they ke maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! meri tauba (jange-Tabook mein na janey ki) qabool honey ka shukraana ye hai ke main apna maal Allah aur uske rasool ke rastey mein dee-doon. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar apne maal ka aik hissey apne paas hi baqi rakho to tumharey haq mein ye behtar hai. maine arz kya ke phir main apna khaibar ka hissa apne paas mehfooz rakhta hun."
2758,"ye riwayat unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se ki hai ke unhon-ne bayan kya (jab sura Aale-Imran ki) ye aayat nazil huii (لن تنالوا البر حتى تنفقوا مما تحبون) ''tum neki hargiz nahi pa saktey jab tak us maal mein se kharch na karo jo tum ko zyada pasand hai.'' to abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ya Rasulullah! Allah tabarak w taala apni kitab mein farmata hai (لن تنالوا البر حتى تنفقوا مما تحبون) ''tum neki hargiz nahi pa saktey jab tak us maal mein se kharch na karo jo tum ko zyada pasand hai.'' aur mere amwaal mein sabse pasand mujhey beerhaa hai. bayan kya ke beerhaa aik baagh tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi usmein tashrif ley jaya kartey, iske saaey mein baithtey aur uska pani peetey (abu-Talha ne kaha ke) isliye wo izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ki raah mein sadqa aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye hai. main uski neki aur uske zakheerae-aakhirat honey ki ummeed rakhta hun. isliye ya Rasulullah ! jis tarah Allah aapko bataaey usey kharch keejiye. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya waah! waah, shaabaash! abu-Talha ye to bada nafa bakhsh maal hai, ham tum se usey qabool karke phir tumharey hi hawale kar detey hain aur ab tum usey apne azeezon ko de-do. chunanche abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne wo baagh apne azeezon ko de diya. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jin logon ko baagh aap ne diya tha unmein Ubaii aur Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) they. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna hissey Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko bech diya to kisi ne unse kaha ke kya aap abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka diya hua maal beech rahe ho? Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke main khajoor ka aik saa roopon ke aik saa ke badal kyon na bechoon. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ye baagh bani Hadeela ke mohalle ke qareeb tha jisey Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne (bataur qile' ke) tameer kya tha."
2759,"kuchh log guman karne lagey hain ke ye aayat (jis zikr unwaan mein hua) meeraas ki aayat mansukh ho gaee hai, nahi qism Allah ki aayat mansukh nahi hui albatta log is par amal karne mein sust ho gaey hain. tarkey ke leney waley 2 tarah ke hotey hain aik wo jo waaris hon unko hissey diya jaeyga doosrey wo jo waaris na hon unko narmii se jawab dene ka hukm hai. wo yun kahey miyan main tum ko dene ka ikhtiyar nahi rakhta ."
2760,"aik sahabi (Sa'd bin Ubaada) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke meri walida ki maut achcha waaqe ho gaee, mera khayal hai ke agar unhein guftgu ka mauqa milta to wo sadqa kartin to kya main unki taraf se khairat kar sakta hoon? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya haan unki taraf se khairat kar."
2761,"Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se masla poochha, unhon-ne arz kya ke meri maan ka intiqal ho gaya hai aur uske zimme aik nazar thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unki taraf se nazar poori kar de."
2762,qabila banii-Saaida ke bhai Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ki maan ka intiqal hua to wo unki khidmat mein hazir nahi they (balke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jang daumatul-Jandal mein Sharik they) isliye wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur arz kya ya Rasulullah! meri walida ka intiqal ho gaya hai aur main us waqt maujood nahi tha to agar main unki taraf se khairat karun to unhein iska fayda pahunchega? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan! Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke main aapko gawah banata hun ke mera baagh Mikhraaf naam ke unki taraf se khairat hai.
2763,"unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aayat (وإن خفتم أن لا تقسطوا في اليتامى فانكحوا ما طاب لكم من النساء) ''aur agar tum daro ke yatimon ke haq mein insaf nahi karogey to (aur) aurton mein se jo tumhen pasand hon unse nikah kar lo.'' ka matlab puchha to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya ke us se murad wo yateem ladki hai jo apne wali ki zer parwarish ho, phir wali ke dil mein uska Husn aur uske maal ki taraf se raghbate-nikaah paida ho jaey magar us kam mehar par jo waisii ladkiyon ka hona chahiye to is tarah nikah karne se rokaa gaya lekin ye ke wali unke sath poorey mehar ki adaaeygi mein insaf se kaam lein (to nikah kar saktey hain) aur unhein ladkiyon ke siwa dusri aurton se nikah karne ka hukm diya gaya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha to izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne ye aayat nazil farmai ( ويستفتونك في Nisa قل الله يفتيكم فيهن‏ ( '' aap se log aurton ke mutaalliq poochhtey hain aap keh dein ke Allah tumhen unke barey mein hidayat karta hai.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke phir Allah Taala ne is aayat mein bayan kar diya ke yateem ladki agar khoobsurat aur maal wali ho aur (unke wali) unse nikah karne ke khaahishmand hon lekin pura mehar dene mein unke ( khandan ke) tariqon ki pabandi na kar sakein to (wo unse nikah mat karein ( jabke maal aur Husn ki kami ki wjah se unki taraf unhein koi raghbat na hoti ho to unhein wo chhod detey aur unke siwa kisi dusri aurat ko talash kartey. rawi ne kaha jis tarah aisey log raghbat na honey ki sura mein un yateem ladkiyon ko chhod detey, isi tarah unke liye ye bhi jaaiz nahi ke jab un ladkiyon ki taraf unhein raghbat ho to unke poorey mehar ke mamley main aur unke huquq ada karne mein insaf se kaam liye baghair unse nikah karein."
2764,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni aik jaaidaad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein waqf kar di, us jaaidaad ka naam samagh tha aur ye aik khajoor ka aik baagh tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! mujhey aik jaaidaad mili hai aur mere khayal mein bahut hi umda hai, isliye maine chaha ke usey sadqa kar dun to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke asl maal ko sadqa karke na bechaa ja sakey na hiba kya ja sakey aur na iska koi waaris bin sakey, sirf iska phal (Allah ki raah mein) kharch ho. chunanche umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey sadqa kar diya, unka ye sadqa ghaziyon ke liye, ghulam aazad karaaney ke liye, mohtajon aur kamzoron ke liye, musaafiron ke liye aur rishtedaron ke liye tha aur ye ke iske nigraan ke liye usmein koi muzaayqa nahi hoga ke wo dastoor ke muwafiq usmein se khaaey ya apne kisi dost ko khilaey basharte ke usmein se maal jama karne ka irada na rakhta ho."
2765,"(Qur'aan Majeed ki us aayat) ومن كان غنيا فليستعفف ومن كان فقيرا فليأكل بالمعروف ''aur jo shakhs maaldaar ho wo apne ko yateem ke maal se bilkul rokey rakhey, albatta jo shakhs naadaar ho to wo dastoor ke mutabiq kha sakta hai'' ke barey mein farmaya ke yatimon ke waliyon ke barey mein nazil hui ke yateem ke maal mein se agar wali naadaar ho to dastoor ke mutabiq iske maal mein se ley sakta hai."
2766,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''saat (7) gunahon se jo tabah kar dene waley hain bachtey raho. ''sahaaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha ya Rasulullah! wo kon se gunah hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik thahraanaa, jadoo karnaa, kisi ki nahaq jaan lena ke jisey Allah Taala ne haram qarar diya hai, sood khaanaa, yateem ka maal khaanaa, ladai mein se bhag jaana, paak daman bhuli bhaalii eman wali aurton par tohmat lagaanaa.''"
2767,"ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko koi wasii banata to wo kabhi inkar na kartey. Ibne-Sirin Taabai (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ka mahboob mashghala ye tha ke yateem ke maal w jaaidaad ke silsiley mein unke khair-khaahon aur waliyon ko jama kartey taake unke liye koi achi sura paida karne ke liye ghaur karein. Taaus Taabai (Rahmatullahi-alaih) se jab yatimon ke barey mein koi sawal kya jata to aap ye aayat padhtey ke) والله يعلم المفسد من المصلح‏ ( ''aur Allah fasaad paida karne waley aur sanwaarney waley ko khub janta hai.'' ata (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne yatimon ke barey mein kaha chahe wo maamooli qism ke logon mein hon ya badey darjey ke, uska wali uske hisse mein se jaisey uske laaiq ho, waisaa is par kharch kare."
2768,"ham se Yaqoob-bin-Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) bin Kasir ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Ismaaeel-bin-Ulaih ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Abdul-Azeez bin-Suhaib ne bayan kya, unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madiney tashrif laey to unke sath koi khaadim nahi tha. isliye abu-Talha (jo mere sauteley bap they) mera hath pakadkar Rasulullah ki khidmat me ley gaey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool Anas ek samajhdaar bachchaa hai, ye aapki khidmat kiya karega. Hazrat Anas kahtey hain ki maine aapkey sath safar or qiyam donon me khidmatki, aapney mujhsey kabhi kisi kaam ke barey me jisey maine kar diya ho, ye nahi farmaya ki ye kaam tumney is tarah kyon kiya? isi tarah kisi aise kaam ke barey me jisey main na kar saka hun aapney ye nahi Farmaya ki tooney ye kaam is tarah kyaon nahi kiya?"
2769,"abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) khajoor ke baghaat ke eitibaar se Madina ke Ansar mein sabse badey maaldaar they aur unhein apne tamam maalon mein masjide-Nabawi ke samney beerhaa ka baagh sabse zyada pasand tha. khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi us baagh mein tashrif ley jatey aur iska meethaa pani peetey they. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir jab ye aayat nazil huii ( لن تنالوا البر حتى تنفقوا مما تحبون‏ ) ''nekii tum hargiz nahi hasil karogey jab tak apne us maal se na kharch karo jo tumhen pasand hon.'' to abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) uthey aur aa kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! Allah Taala farmata hai ( لن تنالوا البر حتى تنفقوا مما تحبون‏ ) ''tum neki hargiz nahi hasil kar sakogey jab tak apne un maalon mein se na kharch karo jo tumhen zyada pasand hon.'' aur mere maalon mein mujhey sabse zyada pasand beerhaa hai aur ye Allah ke raaste mein sadqa hai, main Allah ki bargah se uski neki aur zakheera aakhirat honey ki ummeed rakhta hun. aapko jahan Allah Taala bataaey usey kharch karein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya shaabaash ye to bada fayda bakhsh maal hai ya aap ne bajaey ( رابح ( رابع ke) رايح ( kaha ye shak Abdullaah-bin-Muslima rawi ko hua tha. aur jo kuchh tum ne kaha maine sab sun liya hai aur mera khayal hai ke tum usey apne naatey walon ko de do. abu-Talha ne arz kya ya Rasulullah! main aisa hi karunga. chunanche unhon-ne apne azeezon aur apne chacha ke ladkon mein taqseem kar diya. Ismaaeel, Abdullah-bin Yusuf aur Yahya-bin-Yahya ne Malik ke waastey se. ( رابح (ke bajaey ( رايح ( bayan kya hai."
2770,aik sahabi Sad-bin-Ubada ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke unki maan ka intiqal ho gaya hai. kya agar wo unki taraf se khairat karein to unhein iska fayda pahunchega? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab diya ke haan. is par un sahabi ne kaha ke mera mewon se bharaa aik baagh hai aur main aapko gawah banata hun ke maine wo unki taraf se sadqa kar diya.
2771,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (Madina mein) masjid banaaney ka hukm diya aur bani najaar se farmaya tum apne us baagh ka mujh se mol kar lo. unhon-ne kaha ke hargiz nahi Allah ki qism ham to Allah hi se iska mol lengey.
2772,"ham se musaddad-bin-Musarhid ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Yazeed bin Zaree ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Abdullaah-bin-A'un (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya unse Naafe ne aur unse Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke umr ko Khaibar me ek zameen mili to aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat me hazir hue aur kaha ki mujhey ek zameen mili hai or issey behtar maal mujhey kabhi nahi mila tha, aap iskey barey me mujhe kya mashwaraa dete hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Farmaya ki ""agar chahey to asal jaayedaad apne qabzey me rakh ley aur uskey nafey aur faaydey ko khairat kar dey."" chunaanchey umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey us shart par sadqaa (waqf) kar diya ki asal zameen n bechii jaey, na tohfey me di jaey, n viraasat mein kisi ko miley or faqeeron, rishtedaaron, ghulaamon ko aazad karaaney, Allah ke rastey (key mujaahidon) mehmaanon or musaafiron ke liye ye zameen waqf hai. jo shakhs bhi iska mutawalli (zimmedaar) ho agar dastoor ke mutabiq ismein se khaae ya apney kisi dost ko khilaey to koi haraj nahi, bashartey ki maal ko jama karney ka irada na ho."
2773,"ham se abu-Aasim ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ham se Abdullaah-bin-A'un ne bayan kya, unse Naafe ne bayan kya, unse Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko Khaibar me ek jaaydaad mili to aap Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat me hazir hokar uskey barey me khabar di. pyaarey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar chaho to usey sadqaa kar do. chunaanchey Hazrat umr ne usey faqeeron, miskeenon, rishtedaron or mehmaanon ke liye usey sadqaa kar diya."
2774,"ham se Ishaq-bin-Mansur ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Abdus-Samad ne bayan kya, kaha ke maine apne walid (abdul-Waaris) se suna, unse Abu-Tayyah ne bayan kya, kaha ke mujh se Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jab pyaarey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina tashrif laey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid banaaney ke liye hukm diya aur farmaya : ""aey banu-Najjaar! apney baagh ki mujhsey qeemat le lo."" unhoney kaha ki nahi, Allah ki qasam! ham to iski qeemat sirf Allah se maangtey hain."
2775,"mujh se Naafe ne bayan kya, aur unse Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna aik ghoda Allah ke rastey mein (jihad karne ke liye) aik aadmi ko de diya. ye ghoda Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne diya tha, taake Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jihad mein kisi ko is par Sawar karein. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko malum hua ke jis shakhs ko ye ghoda mila tha, wo us ghodey ko bazar mein bech raha hai. isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke kya wo usey khareed saktey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hargiz usey na khareed. apna diya hua sadqa wapas na ley."
2776,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo aadmi mere waaris hain, jo rupya ashrafii agar main chhod jaun to wo taqseem na karein, wo meri beeviyon ka kharch aur jaaidaad ka ehtimaam karne waley ka kharch nikalney ke baad sadqa hai.''"
2777,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne waqf mein ye shart lagai thi ke iska mutwallii usmein se kha sakta hai aur apne dost ko khilaa sakta hai lekin wo daulat na jodey.
2778,"Abdaan ne bayan kya ke mujhey mere walid ne khabar di, unhein Shoba ne, unhein Abu-Ishaq ne, unhein abu-Abdur-Rehman ne ke jab Hazrat Usman ghanii (Raziallahu anhu) ka gheraaw kar liya gaya to (apney ghar key) uper chadhkar aapney baaghiyon se kaha ki main tumko khuda ki qasam dekar poochhta hun aur sirf Nabi Karim ke sahaabiyon se qism dekar poochhta hun ki kya aap logon ko malum nahi hai ki jab Allah ke rasool ne farmaya ""jo shakhs Roomaa kuney ko khodeygaa aur usey musalmaanon ke liye waqf kar dega to usey jannat ki khushkhabri hai."" to maine hi us kuney ko khodaa tha. kya aap logon ko malum nahii hai ki pyaare Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab Farmaya tha ki ""ghazwaaey-Tabook par jaanewaaley (Jaishe-Usrat) ko jo shakhs saazo-saamaan se lais kar dega to usey jannat ki khushkhabri hai"" to maine hi usey lais kiya tha. rawi ne bayan kiya ki aapkii in baton ki sabney tasdeeq ki thi. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne waqf ke barey me farmaya tha ki iska intizam karnewaalaa agar ismein so khaaey to koi haraj nahi hai. zahir hai ki muntazim khud wo bhi ho sakta hai jisey waqf kiya gaya hai or kabhi doosrey bhi ho saktey hain or har ek ke liye ye jaayez hai."
2779,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ''aey banu-Najjaar! tum apne baagh ki qeemat mujh se wsool kar lo to unhon-ne arz kya ke ham uski qeemat Allah Taala ke siwa kisi se nahi chaahtey.''
2780,"banii-Saham ka aik shakhs Tameem daari aur Adii-bin-Badaa ke sath safar ko nikla, wo aisey mulk mein ja kar mar gaya jahan koi musalman na tha. ye donon shakhs uska chhoda hua maal lekar Madina wapas aaey. uske saman mein chandi ka aik glaas gum tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un donon ko qism khaney ka hukm farmaya (unhon-ne qism kha lii) phir aisa hua ke wo glaas Makka mein mila, unhon-ne kaha ham ne ye glaas Tameem aur Adi se khareedaa hai. us waqt maiyat ke 2 azeez (Amr-bin-al-Aas aur muttalib khadey huey aur unhon-ne qism khaaii ke ye hamari gawahi Tameem aur Adi ki gawahi se zyada moa'tabar hai, ye glaas maiyat hi ka hai. Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha un hi ke barey mein ye aayat nazil hui (ya أيها الذين آمنوا شهادة بينكم‏ ( aakhir aayat tak."
2781,"unke walid (Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu)) Uhud ki ladai mein Shahid ho gaey they. apne peechhey chh ladkiyan chhodi thin aur qarz bhii. jab khajoor ke phal todney ka waqt aaya to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya ya Rasulullah! aapko ye malum hi hai ke mere walid maajid Uhud ki ladai mein Shahid ho chukey hain aur bahut zyada qarz chhod gaey hain, main chahta tha ke qarz-khaah aapko dekh lein (taake qarz mein kuchh riaayat kar dein) lekin wo Yahudi they aur wo nahi maaney, isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jao aur khaliyiaan mein har qism ki khajoor alag-alag kar lo jab maine aisa kar liya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bulaayaa, qarz-khaahon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh kar aur zyada sakhti shuru kar di thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab ye tarze-amal dekha to sabse badey khajoor ke dher ke gird Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen chakkar lagaey aur wahin baith gaey phir farmaya ke apne qarz-khaahon ko bulaao. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne naap-naap kar dena shuru kya aur Allah ki qism mere walid ki tamam amanat ada kar di, Allah gawah hai ke main itney par bhi razi tha ke Allah Taala mere walid ka tamam qarz ada kar de aur main apni bahnon ke liye aik khajoor bhi usmein se na ley jaun lekin hua ye ke dher ke dher bach rahe aur maine dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jis dher par baithey huey they usmein se to aik khajoor bhi nahi di gaee thi. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke) أغروا بي ( (hadees mein alfaaz) ke mana hain ke mujh par bhadakney aur sakhti karne lagey. usi mana mein Quran Majeed ki aayat ( فأغرينا بينهم العداوة والبغضاء ( main ( فأغرينا ( hai."
